data.description: Welcome to this custom home nestled on a beautiful, wooded lot in prestigious Prestonwood Estates of North Arlington. This home showcases a versatile floor plan and offers many updates and amenities. Two large living rooms each with a fireplace plus a game room at the front of the home provides the new owners many possibilities. The spacious downstairs owner's suite offers split vanities, separate shower and oversized tub plus walk-in closets. Two secondary bedrooms with a hall bath complete the downstairs bedroom wing. Upstairs 4th bedroom-space+multi-level deck overlooks the private backyard. Welcome home!!
